  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>An excellent recently remodelled and totally renovated modern hotel in a highly scenic and very convenient elevated ski-in/ski-out position. Its popular à la carte restaurant offers international and Lappish specialities, as well as simpler fare such as burgers and pizzas. The Glacier bar and lounge is a great place to relax at the end of the day and the Ski Bistro forms the hub of après-ski with DJ music, karaoke and occasional live music. Guests can pamper themselves in the hotel's Pyhä Klubi fitness room and sauna. The hotel is situated right next to the ski slopes, ski school and ski hire shop with panoramic views overlooking magnificent national park scenery.</span></p>]]></description>
