  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>All our modern refurbished twin-bedded rooms have magnificent fell views, shower, wc, drying closet, hairdryer and flat-screen TV. No single occupancy supplement 8-21 Dec &amp; 5 Jan-2 Mar.</li>
<li>Spacious Family Rooms sleep a 3rd or 4th person on 2 single pull-out sofa beds, and have a fridge and tea/coffee making facilities in addition.</li>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/laplandfinland/pyha/pyhae-ski-inn-suites/">Pyhä Ski-Inn Suites</a>:</strong> 48 Superior attractively priced suites located 75m from main hotel and ideal for couples or families. See separate description. <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/laplandfinland/pyha/pyhae-ski-inn-suites/">For full description see here</a>.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
